description: Annual Christmas mapping event. This pack features 19 small maps in varying styles where all gameplay takes place within a 1024x1024x1024 space. It runs on Arcane Dimensions 1.8 (included) and comes with some additional content like sounds, models, skyboxes and music tracks. The map sources are included.
notes: These maps require a source port with increased limits + BSP2 support.
title: Xmas Jam 2020
